track_name: Wicked Games (feat. Anna Naklab) - Radio Edit

data.prompt: A dreamlike, ethereal scene unfolds in a moonlit forest, where shimmering particles dance through the air like fireflies, accompanied by soft, pulsating lights that resonate with the beat of a hidden rhythm. The warm hues of amber and gold blend with the cool shades of blue, evoking a sense of enchantment and whimsy.

A surreal, abstract cityscape rises against a twilight sky, where vibrant neon colors swirl and flow like liquid, encapsulating the electrifying energy of the night. Shadows of half-formed figures twist and twirl, hinting at untold stories woven into the fabric of an adventurous evening.

A captivating portrait emerges of a figure entranced in motion, their silhouette subtly illuminated by colorful city lights that reflect the pulse of the electronic beat. A soft haze envelops them, embodying a joyous blend of freedom and mystery, as if they are dancing between the realms of reality and fantasy.
